svg.script: function init(event) { if ( window.svgDocument == null ) { svgDocument = event.target.ownerDocument; } } function ShowTooltip(obj) { var cur = obj.id.split("_")[1]; var tip = svgDocument.getElementById('mytooltip_' + cur); tip.setAttribute('visibility', "visible") } function HideTooltip(obj) { var cur = obj.id.split("_")[1]; var tip = svgDocument.getElementById('mytooltip_' + cur); tip.setAttribute('visibility', "hidden") }
